- 1.4.7 version</li>\n            </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.0.7 - Released: Apr 28, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Updated: Text Domain</li>\n                <li>Fix: minor bugs</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.6 - Released: Apr 14, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fix: Prevent notice on products loop</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.5 - Released: Apr 13, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>New: WordPress 4.5 support</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.4 - Released: Apr 12, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fix: Request a quote button not working in the products loop</li>\n                <li>Fix: Removed unuseless query execution</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.3 - Released: Apr 09, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>New: WPML support</li>\n				<li>Fix: Options total price was not correct when user change quantity on single product page</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.2 - Released: Apr 04, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fix: Options are not saved when a quote was inserted inside a label</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released: Apr 01, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fix: Price total doesn\' t change after option is selected on quick view</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released: Mar 31, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Initial Release</li>\n            </ul>\n		\n    \";}', 'no'),
