(583, 43, 'they_say_0_say', 'Got some Halloween decorations and themed cupcakes for my sons birthday celebration during Halloween. Thankfully, my sons friends also enjoyed the party and food. Generally a great experience with Party Fairy, especially the service provided. Would recommend to other parents who wants to plan a party but unsure where to look.'),
