(7286, 441, 'they_say_0_say', 'Got some Halloween decorations and themed cupcakes for my sons birthday celebration during Halloween. Thankfully, my sons friends also enjoyed the party and food. Generally a great experience with Party Fairy, especially the service provided. Would recommend to other parents who wants to plan a party but unsure where to look.'),
(7287, 441, '_they_say_0_say', 'field_5cc1722fd2a83'),
(7288, 441, 'they_say_0_by', 'Mr Christian Pang'),
(7289, 441, '_they_say_0_by', 'field_5cc17224d2a82'),
(7290, 441, 'list_0_title', 'Considerations to Make When Finding the Best Party Supplies in Singapore'),
(7291, 441, '_list_0_title', 'field_5cc17681ce773'),
(7292, 441, 'list_0_description', 'For most people, hosting a party is something they love doing. Being in charge of hosting an event like this can be fun and rewarding. A key component in throwing a great shindig is finding the Best party supplies in Singapore.\r\n\r\nWith all of the suppliers out there, it can be difficult to find the best birthday party supplies for a reasonable price. Trying to rush through this buying process can lead to a number of mistakes being made. Before trying to figure out where to buy party supplies in Singapore, here are some of the things a person will need to consider.'),
(7293, 441, '_list_0_description', 'field_5cc17686ce774'),
(7294, 441, 'list_1_title', 'What Is Needed?'),
(7295, 441, '_list_1_title', 'field_5cc17681ce773'),
(7296, 441, 'list_1_description', 'The first decision a person needs to make before going out to shop is what supplies are needed. Often times, the supplies a person will need for a party will be based on the theme. If a person is hosting a child\'s birthday party, getting things like balloons and streamers will be essential.\r\n\r\nOnce a person has decided on a theme for their party, they can get wholesale party supplies to bring their ideas to life. A reputable party supply company will be able to help an individual find the best possible items for their gathering.'),
(7297, 441, '_list_1_description', 'field_5cc17686ce774'),
(7298, 441, 'list_2_title', 'Setting A Budget Is Important'),
(7299, 441, '_list_2_title', 'field_5cc17681ce773'),
(7300, 441, 'list_2_description', 'Before going to shop for party supplies, a person will also need to think about how much money they can logically spend. The last thing anyone wants is to overextend their finances due to a lack of planning. Checking out online store in Singapore for party supplies can help a person get an idea of how much they are going to have to spend on their party.\r\n\r\nOnline research is also a great way for a person to find the best supplier of party supplies in their area. With the information from a company\'s website, a person can decide whether or not they are the right fit.\r\n\r\nRushing through this research process can lead to a person paying too much for the party decorations they need. With a bit of time and effort, a person can find what they need and get it delivered in a matter of days.'),
(7301, 441, '_list_2_description', 'field_5cc17686ce774'),
(7302, 441, 'list_3_title', 'Why Party Fairy?'),
(7303, 441, '_list_3_title', 'field_5cc17681ce773'),
(7304, 441, 'list_3_description', 'With Party Fairy - being a one-stop online store for Parties, you will have access to a myriad of party supplies - from delicious cakes to delectable dessert tables, from themed balloons to customised paper plates - We have them all!\r\n\r\nSo whether you\'re planning for a small party or a festive gathering - We have you covered! No more travelling all over Singapore to get your ideal decor. No more waiting for countless deliveries from various vendors. Get your party supplies today!'),
(7305, 441, '_list_3_description', 'field_5cc17686ce774'),
(7306, 441, 'they_say_1_say', 'Got some Halloween decorations and themed cupcakes for my sons birthday celebration during Halloween. Thankfully, my sons friends also enjoyed the party and food. Generally a great experience with Party Fairy, especially the service provided. Would recommend to other parents who wants to plan a party but unsure where to look.'),
